#: includes/class-cma-analyzer.php:1406
msgid "Define primary content, then merge or redirect overlapping content."
msgstr ""
"Définissez un contenu principal, puis fusionnez ou redirigez les contenus "
"qui se chevauchent."

#: includes/class-cma-analyzer.php:1410
msgid ""
"Reorient content toward a different intent and use more distinct internal "
"anchors."
msgstr ""
"Réorientez un contenu vers une intention différente et utilisez des ancres "
"internes plus distinctes."

#: includes/class-cma-analyzer.php:1414
msgid ""
"Strengthen links to the primary content and differentiate links to the "
"secondary content."
msgstr ""
"Renforcez le maillage vers le contenu principal et différenciez les liens "
"vers le contenu secondaire."

#: includes/class-cma-analyzer.php:1418
msgid ""
"Update H1 headings or SEO titles to clearly separate each content intent."
msgstr ""
"Modifiez les H1 ou les titres SEO pour séparer clairement l’intention de "
"chaque contenu."

#: includes/class-cma-analyzer.php:1421
msgid ""
"Monitor only, or add differentiating internal links if rankings overlap."
msgstr ""
"Surveillez uniquement, ou ajoutez des liens internes différenciants si les "
"positions se chevauchent."

#: includes/class-cma-analyzer.php:1426
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Risk score %1$d/100 based on: %2$s. This content may send overly similar "
